name: UFO Ocean Frenzy
description:
Your mission was simple: disintegrate cows on earth for research purposes. Being your first flight outside your planet though, you have no idea how cows look, so you ended up in an ocean and fish look just like cows in your alien mind...

Controls: Arrow keys to move, X to shoot, Z to restart when you die

Kill fish gives you +1 score but killing turtles deducts -5 from your score!

Avoid the rokets and post your score in the comments!

This  game was made in 3 days using PICO-8 for the Mini Jam 91
